AddFromFile(TFileName)

This procedure Adds a New Record and ask it to load a File. If File Exists. I then checks if upload is 'True' and then stores it to the list. If AutoSave is on and Storage is Set it can also try to store then new record and Retrieve the new 'ID' from the Storage.
